An open-source and free wallet implementation for the Android runtime, based on [[bitcoinj|BitCoinJ]]. It requires either Android 2.3 (or newer) or Black Berry OS 10 (or newer). It was first released on March 7, 2011 (1.1). As of April 2013, it is being used by 50.000 people.

